> +
> +    /*
> +     * Wire the outputs from each CPU's generic timer and the GICv3
> +     * maintenance interrupt signal to the appropriate GIC PPI inputs,
> +     * and the GIC's IRQ/FIQ/VIRQ/VFIQ interrupt outputs to the CPU's inputs.
